00:28:21,549 --> 00:28:23,033
It's not gonna be you, April.

505
00:28:23,135 --> 00:28:24,629
I don't care how
many boxes you check,

506
00:28:24,653 --> 00:28:26,420
you're not gonna
be chief resident.

507
00:28:26,522 --> 00:28:28,522
Three-O Vicryl.

