00:29:11,450 --> 00:29:14,952
Lucy and I... It's new.

517
00:29:15,054 --> 00:29:16,787
Why?

518
00:29:16,889 --> 00:29:19,422
Because I don't want the person
that I recommend to pull a me

519
00:29:19,524 --> 00:29:21,444
and go running back to
the girl they left behind.

520
00:29:21,543 --> 00:29:26,680
So just... make sure you
know what you're doing.

521
00:29:26,781 --> 00:29:29,349
Or else you'll have
me to answer to.

522
00:29:42,764 --> 00:29:44,431
Admit it.

523
00:29:44,533 --> 00:29:48,802
You saw how good this baby looked on
me so you had to go get one of your own.

524
00:29:48,904 --> 00:29:50,837
Everything's a competition.

525
00:29:50,939 --> 00:29:53,940
- How'd her surgery go?
- Robbins said she's fine.

526
00:29:54,059 --> 00:29:55,759
- She's feeding again.
- Good.

