00:30:16,331 --> 00:30:19,065
usually give those things out.

534
00:30:20,602 --> 00:30:23,035
You're both surgeons.
You'd make good parents.

535
00:30:23,138 --> 00:30:24,404
They're gonna see that.

536
00:30:24,506 --> 00:30:26,401
We'd be naive to get
ahead of ourselves.

537
00:30:26,425 --> 00:30:30,543
You're Derek Shepherd. There's a reason
I've been jealous of you my whole life,

538
00:30:30,646 --> 00:30:33,980
and it's not your hair.
You're gonna be OK.

539
00:30:34,082 --> 00:30:39,503
Even Sofia knows that. Right,
Sofia? Say hi to Uncle Derek.

540
00:30:39,605 --> 00:30:42,155
That's Zola's daddy.
Yes, he is. Right?

541
00:30:42,257 --> 00:30:44,057
Ohh.

542
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:47,327
- I'm gonna go feed her.
- Mm.

