the way that my mother raised me.

547
00:31:09,435 --> 00:31:13,269
She didn't bake.

548
00:31:13,371 --> 00:31:18,909
She wasn't a bake-sale mom,
and I... plan on baking all the time.

549
00:31:20,145 --> 00:31:22,629
How about you
tell me about Zola?

550
00:31:22,731 --> 00:31:28,101
Well, Zola had already had a
shunt and spina bifida surgery,

551
00:31:28,203 --> 00:31:30,937
and then we realized
she had this hernia.

552
00:31:31,040 --> 00:31:35,408
And today in her surgery, it
looked like she might go into SVT.

553
00:31:35,510 --> 00:31:40,246
And just as the anesthesiologist
was about to push the adenosine,

554
00:31:40,348 --> 00:31:42,348
it's like she knew to stop,

555
00:31:42,450 --> 00:31:47,704
and her heart just slowed down
all by itself and she went into sinus.

556
00:31:49,858 --> 00:31:54,027
I... I'm sorry. That's not
what you asked me, right?

