knew where she was every second.

571
00:32:51,954 --> 00:32:54,120
I appreciate you
sharing that with me.

572
00:33:02,363 --> 00:33:03,930
I was showing initiative!

573
00:33:04,032 --> 00:33:07,133
That doesn't mean you get to
pretend that you're an attending!

574
00:33:07,235 --> 00:33:08,846
I wasn't pretending, I just
didn't need an attending.

575
00:33:08,870 --> 00:33:11,621
- Oh, my God!
- Teddy is doing
a disservice to me,

576
00:33:11,724 --> 00:33:13,484
and to the education
that I deserve.

577
00:33:13,508 --> 00:33:16,209
I had no choice but to take
my learning into my own hands.

578
00:33:16,311 --> 00:33:18,595
So I took the initiative
and treated a patient

579
00:33:18,697 --> 00:33:20,781
and followed through
to a successful outcome.

580
00:33:20,883 --> 00:33:23,761
If that doesn't show the qualities of a
chief resident, I don't know what does.

581
00:33:23,785 --> 00:33:26,345
You're not gonna
be the chief resident.

582
00:33:27,288 --> 00:33:30,456
It's not gonna
be you. I'm sorry.

583
00:33:32,193 --> 00:33:34,127
Is this from the
chief, or from Teddy?

584
00:33:34,229 --> 00:33:36,145
No, it's from me.

585
00:33:38,283 --> 00:33:41,684
You real... You know
how important this is.

586
00:33:41,786 --> 00:33:44,665
Chief resident can make your career.
You have your pick of fellowships...

587
00:33:44,689 --> 00:33:46,117
You never had
the qualifications.

588
00:33:46,141 --> 00:33:48,108
- Based on what?!
- Chief resident is more

589
00:33:48,210 --> 00:33:53,063
than just a resume boost. It's
managing schedules, overseeing interns,

590
00:33:53,165 --> 00:33:56,032
pushing papers, working
within the system. That isn't you.

591
00:33:56,134 --> 00:33:58,351
- It's never been you.
- I'm protesting this!

592
00:33:58,453 --> 00:34:01,221
- You are screwing
with my career.
- And it will kill you!

593
00:34:01,323 --> 00:34:03,106
You're a surgeon.

594
00:34:03,208 --> 00:34:06,342
Anything that keeps you from
being a surgeon will hurt you,

595
00:34:06,445 --> 00:34:08,456
and it will make you
crazy. We saw it today.

596
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:10,930
You're not built for this job.

597
00:34:11,032 --> 00:34:12,960
You will hate it and
you will resent it,

598
00:34:12,984 --> 00:34:18,288
you will fight against it until
you fail. So just be a surgeon.

599
00:34:19,340 --> 00:34:20,974
You know, it's what you are.

600
00:34:21,076 --> 00:34:24,327
Just be excellent
at what you are.

601
00:34:26,514 --> 00:34:30,616
- Are you done?
- Yes.

602
00:34:30,719 --> 00:34:32,102
Thank you for your time.

603
00:34:39,861 --> 00:34:41,728
I'm not going to Africa.

604
00:34:43,532 --> 00:34:46,098
- Right. Let me just say this...
- No. It's the right thing.

605
00:34:46,201 --> 00:34:51,037
I can finish my residency and then
maybe we can both go to Africa together...

606
00:34:51,139 --> 00:34:54,040
- Alex, I just... Just listen to me.
- You were right this morning.

607
00:34:54,142 --> 00:34:58,694
You said there were other factors
to consider. And you are a factor.

608
00:34:58,796 --> 00:35:01,598
I'm sorry I didn't
say that sooner.

609
00:35:01,700 --> 00:35:04,267
When Robbins said they were
looking for someone single...

