613
00:35:17,465 --> 00:35:19,899
You were right, this morning.

614
00:35:20,001 --> 00:35:22,802
Career comes first.
It's how it should be.

615
00:35:23,805 --> 00:35:26,773
And so I... I took the job.

616
00:35:26,875 --> 00:35:30,693
- So call them. Call Baylor...
- At Namboze.

617
00:35:30,795 --> 00:35:33,929
I took the job at
Namboze Clinic.

618
00:35:34,032 --> 00:35:39,252
You what? My job?
You took my job?

619
00:35:39,354 --> 00:35:41,674
Like you said,
it's not personal.

620
00:35:42,523 --> 00:35:45,391
Sometimes you
have to be a shark.

621
00:36:00,975 --> 00:36:04,043
