639
00:37:04,622 --> 00:37:05,983
- Sir...
- Such a bonehead move,

640
00:37:06,007 --> 00:37:07,284
that I started thinking,

641
00:37:07,308 --> 00:37:09,375
maybe the chief's
trial is flawed.

642
00:37:09,477 --> 00:37:12,879
So I looked into it myself.

643
00:37:12,981 --> 00:37:14,914
The methodology is flawless.

644
00:37:15,017 --> 00:37:18,818
In fact, it's kind of the
stuff that wins awards.

645
00:37:18,920 --> 00:37:22,656
Big awards. Like
the Harper Avery.

